Abstract = {{There is a need for efficient methods for estimating trends in
   spatio-temporal Earth Observation data. A suitable model for such data
   is a space-varying regression model, where the regression coefficients
   for the spatial locations are dependent. A second order intrinsic
   Gaussian Markov Random Field prior is used to specify the spatial
